    "description": {
      "value": "<div><div><p>At 20th level, you become an avatar of peace. As a bonus action, you gain the following benefits for 1 hour:</p><ul><li>All creatures understand you, and you understand all other creatures regardless of ability to speak or languages known.</li><li>You take half damage to all damage dealt by other creatures (their attacks, spells, and other effects).</li><li>Your Aura of the Guardian also causes any critical hit against creatures of your choice in the area to count as a normal hit instead.</li></ul><p>Once you use this feature, you cannot use it again until you finish a long rest, unless you expend a 5th-level spell slot to use it again.</p></div></div>",
